'''连二次硫酸'''是一种[[硫含氧酸|硫含氧酸]] ，其中硫的氧化态为很低的 +1。它的结构为 HOSSOH，全部原子排成了一条线。 它是[[硫代亚硫酸|硫代亚硫酸]] 的异构体，不过能量较低。 其它异构体包括 HOS(=O)SH，HOS(=S)OH和 HS(=O)<sub>2</sub>SH。[[一氧化二硫|一氧化二硫]]，S<sub>2</sub>O，可以被认为是它的酸酐。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Schmidt|first1=Heinar|last2=Steudel|first2=Ralf|last3=Suelzle|first3=Detlev|last4=Schwarz|first4=Helmut|title=Sulfur compounds. 148. Generation and characterization of dihydroxy disulfide, HOSSOH: the chainlike isomer of thiosulfurous acid|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|date=March 1992|volume=31|issue=6|pages=941–944|doi=10.1021/ic00032a004}}</ref> 不像其它低氧化态的硫的含氧酸，连二次硫酸可以以纯净物存在，由[[硫化氢|硫化氢]]和[[二氧化硫|二氧化硫]]在 −70 °C 下的 [[二氟二氯甲烷|二氟二氯甲烷]]反应而成。<ref name=cofg>{{cite book|last1=Makarov |first1=Sergei V.|last2=Makarova |first2=Anna S.|last3=Silaghi-Dumitrescu |first3=Radu|title=PATAI's Chemistry of Functional Groups|date=2014|chapter=Sulfoxylic and thiosulfurous acids and their dialkoxy derivatives|pages=266–273|doi=10.1002/9780470682531.pat0829|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9780470682531}}</ref>

:H<sub>2</sub>S + SO<sub>2</sub> → H<sub>2</sub>S<sub>2</sub>O<sub>2</sub>

连二次硫酸可能会作为硫代次硫酸的一个互变异构体存在。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Patai|first1=Saul|title=The Chemistry of Peroxides|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9781118412718|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hX3mBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA274|language=en|date=2015-04-20}}</ref>

连二次硫酸的有机衍生物如：二甲氧基二硫、<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Baumeister|first1=Edgar|last2=Oberhammer|first2=Heinz|last3=Schmidt|first3=Heinar|last4=Steudel|first4=Ralf|title=Gas phase structure and vibrational spectra of dimethoxysulfane (CH<sub>3</sub>O)2<sub>S</sub>|journal=Heteroatom Chemistry|date=December 1991|volume=2|issue=6|pages=633–641|doi=10.1002/hc.520020605}}</ref> 二乙酸二硫<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Du|first1=Lin|last2=Yao|first2=Li|last3=Ge|first3=Maofa|title=He I Photoelectron Spectroscopy and Theoretical Investigation on Diaceto Disulfide, CH<sub>3</sub>C(O)OSSOC(O)CH<sub>3</sub>|journal=The Journal of Physical Chemistry A|date=November 2007|volume=111|issue=46|pages=11787–11792|doi=10.1021/jp075164h|pmid=17958404|bibcode=2007JPCA..11111787D}}</ref> 和双（三氟乙酸）二硫<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Zeng|first1=Xiaoqing|last2=Ge|first2=Maofa|last3=Sun|first3=Zheng|last4=Wang|first4=Dianxun|title=Bis(trifluoroaceto) Disulfide (CF3C(O)OSSOC(O)CF3): A HeI Photoelectron Spectroscopy and Theoretical Study|journal=The Journal of Physical Chemistry A|date=May 2006|volume=110|issue=17|pages=5685–5691|doi=10.1021/jp061050e|pmid=16640363|bibcode=2006JPCA..110.5685Z}}</ref> 是存在的。

连二次硫酸的共轭碱有连二次硫酸一氢根(1−) {{chem|HSO|2|−}} 和连二次硫酸根(2−) {{chem|SO|2|2−}}。

==性质==
计算预测它的 S−S 键长为 2.013 Å，O−S 键长 1.645 Å，而 H−O 键长为 0.943 Å。<ref name="tcop">{{cite book|last1=Patai|first1=Saul|title=The Chemistry of Peroxides|date=2004|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9781118412718|page=296|volume=3 part 1|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hX3mBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA296|language=en}}</ref>

==相关化合物==
相关的化合物包括等电子体{{le|四氧化二氢|hydrogen tetroxide}} HOOOOH，[[氧三硫化二氢|氧三硫化二氢]] HOSSSH、 HSOSSH 和 [[四硫化二氢|四硫化二氢]] HSSSSH。

